des: Incorporated in 2012, T.F.S - Total Financing Solutions Inc. was founded by born and raised Vancouverite Sunil Prasad. Beginning his career as a stock investor, Sunil studied and quickly learned how to prudently manage investments in an ever-changing market while still producing exceptional returns. Sunil eventually migrated into the real estate investment industry. Entrenched in the Vancouver market, Sunil began actively purchasing, renovating, and flipping homes with consistent, profitable success.
